		</aside></article><article class="contentArea clearfix"><article class="textRightBar"><article id="post-2267" class="post-2267 page type-page status-publish hentry"><h1 class="entry-title">Closure Information</h1>
<!-- .entry-header -->
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p class="has-text-align-left"><em>This page is being created as a hub for information and updates affecting our school and families as a result of COVID-19. It will be updated with new information as it is available. Thank you for your patience as it is being populated. </em></p>



<p><strong>The school is closed for the remainder of the 2019-2020 school year. Teachers are working to set up lesson plans and will be making contact with students and families regularly.</strong> If you have any questions or concerns, please call the school office at <strong>802-767-4632</strong> and leave a message in the General Mailbox, and someone will return your call as soon as possible. Or, email <a href="mailto:eharrington@wrvsu.org"><strong>eharrington@wrvsu.org</strong></a>. </p>



<h2><span class="has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color">Meals: </span></h2>



<p>All children ages 0-18 are eligible for one free breakfast and one free lunch each day. Please sign up prior to each delivery day.</p>



<p><strong>Schedule:</strong></p>



<p>Monday, Wednesday, Friday – curbside pick up at school 11 a.m.-12 noon. Bus deliveries 11 a.m-1 p.m. on the normal bus routes at select bus stops. There will be two days worth of meals provided on Monday and Wednesday.</p>



<p><strong>PLEASE NOTE: For the week of April 20-24 (Spring Break week), meals are available on Monday and Wednesday only. Wednesday’s pick-up/delivery will have meals for three days, to allow food service some time off on Friday. </strong></p>



<p>If you would like to sign up for meals, please call the office and leave us a message with the number of children, if they have any food allergies, and a callback number if we need to reach you. You can also email <a href="mailto:eharrington@wrvsu.org">eharrington@wrvsu.org</a>.<strong><em> Those not signed up for continuous meals, please advise of additions/changes by 8 p.m. on the evenings before delivery days so the kitchen staff can be sure to have enough meals prepared. </em></strong></p>



<h2>Chromebooks</h2>



<p>A limited number of <strong>Chromebooks</strong> are available for student use during their continuing education at home. Please contact the school office or email <a href="mailto:eharrington@wrvsu.org">eharrington@wrvsu.org</a> to inquire. Due to the limited number, we can offer only one per family at this time. </p>



<h2>Newsletters:</h2>



